@@TJvDateTimePicker.NullDate
Summary
  Indicates the date or time that represents an empty "null" value.
Description
  Use NullDate to specify a date or time - depending on the Kind property - that represents an
  empty "null" value. If the user entered a date or time equal to nulldate, thus the Date or Time 
  property is equal to NullDate, then the string represented by NullText is displayed.
See Also
  DropDownDate, NullText
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvDateTimePicker.NullText
Summary
  Indicates the text to display when Date or Time equals NullDate.
Description
  Use NullText to specify a date or time - depending on the Kind property - that represents the
  text to display when Date or Time equals NullDate. If the user entered a date or time equal to 
  nulldate, thus the Date or Time property is equal to NullDate, then the string represented by 
  NullText is displayed.
See Also
  DropDownDate
